{"tid":1257182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想去626","createTime":"2019-06-25T12:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T15:35:58.000Z","uid":267032,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"24c9b51f8c33a77ca2e7d10b6e82b238258b625f","tid":1257182,"uid":267032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"之前幾次都有去,出到去一個人憨膠膠<br />\n除左嗌下口號又唔知可以做咩 <br />\n望下身邊個個都一班班一pairpair咁<br />\n呢兩日回想下都覺得自己好柒<br />\n好想出一分力但係又敵不過自己心理<br />\n<br />\n利申:毒撚"},{"pid":"153bc6b47631f44d790a8f7469738a759a1be117","tid":1257182,"uid":258416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"大把巴絲自己一個去"},{"pid":"bcd7b7a969428a70209c3cfd98c03a0e79fad513","tid":1257182,"uid":258416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"搵朋友一齊去啦"},{"pid":"2583631d047f2f8a7ce13e90bab0a43f5cbeec1e","tid":1257182,"uid":6111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"除左兩次星期日遊行<br />\n我諗唔到有邊次唔係一班人出到去之後就走散晒"},{"pid":"205634235cb9981c4d1244ea246ca3ffc17c352c","tid":1257182,"uid":194783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"我明<br />\n自己一個行嚟行去<br />\n想幫手又唔敢出聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f5ccd3f72456c7b5fccb56f03430bfc4c67e31","tid":1257182,"uid":165889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"其實好多都係自己一個<br />\n大家又戴曬口罩<br />\n開口大家傾幾句，其實唔需要太大負擔<br />\n行嚟行去又好、坐又好<br />\n出得去已經係出咗力"},{"pid":"d5878fef10b63ceb6cadf261c3a6ad78d5c04ee0","tid":1257182,"uid":7818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"兩次星期日都係一條友去<br />\n次次連登都話大把人單拖去<br />\n次次自己一條友行果時周圍都係幾個人一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我626都係會一條友出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e26f8916188510e866cbdba8efec94c25